value.expression:
SELECT PF.X5FECPRO, PF.X5MSGTY , PF.X5FUNCTCD, PM.G2MOTACC, PF.X5PRIACC, PF.X5PROCCD,
PF.X5TRAAMN, PF.X5TRADCZ, PF.X5ACQREFN, PF.X5TRAID, CONCAT(CONCAT(XECANAME,XECACTRY),XECACITY ), PF.X5NRORCL, PF.X5SECRCL 
FROM QS36F.AEXA05PF PF
JOIN QS36F.AEXM1240 XM ON PF.X5NRORCL=XM.XENRORCL
JOIN QS36F.IPMG02PF PM ON PF.X5NRORCL= PM.G2NRORCL AND PF.X5SECRCL=PM.G2SECRCL
WHERE
PF.X5FECPRO = $vFecha_Proceso$ AND PF.X5TIPPRO = 'O' AND PF.X5NRORCL > 0 AND XM.XEFUNCTCD = 200 AND PF.X5TRAAMN > 0
